    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 117.</p><p>Apparate</p><p>Mobility, Sunyata</p><p>Classes: Monk, Ranger Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 0 LP Range: 500 feet Duration: Instantaneous</p><p>You focus your soul and body to modify your position in space with only a thought, stepping through the void between places. You teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within 500 feet. You can bring one willing creature within 5 feet of you along.</p><p>LP Cost. You can use this Mythical Technique at the end of another creature’s turn by expending 1 Legendary Point.</p></div>",
